metadata.name: The OMG Cat
metadata.description: With over 24 million views on Youtube “The OMG Cat” unexpectedly became a viral sensation for Choco back in 2010 it was featured on several popular tv shows from The Tonight Show with Jimmy Fallon to Justin Bieber in Funny Or Die’s OMG Bieber vs. OMG Cat Youtube video. It became one of the most viral Cat videos on Youtube in 2011, The 18 second viral hit will now be immortalise as its official NFT on the Ethereum Blockchain. 11 years later and the mystery continues, what did the Choco the cat see!
